<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <style>
        html, body {
            height: 100%;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .cont {
            height: 100%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-direction: row;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeIn 2s forwards;
        }
        .column {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            width: 50%;
            transform: translateY(50px);
            animation: slideIn 1s 0.5s forwards;
        }
        img {
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            animation: imgBounce 1s alternate;
        }
        h1, h3 {
            font-family: sans-serif;
            padding-left: 100px;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: textFadeIn 1s forwards;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            animation-delay: 1s;
        }
        h3 {
            height: 70%;
            font-weight: 100;
            font-size: 17px;
            animation-delay: 1.5s;
        }
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            to {
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }
        @keyframes slideIn {
            to {
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
        @keyframes imgBounce {
            from {
                transform: translateY(-10px);
            }

        }
        @keyframes textFadeIn {
            to {
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }
        @media screen and (max-width: 830px) {
            img {
                width: 250px;
                height: 250px;
            }
            .cont {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            .column {
                width: 100%;
            }
            h1 {
                padding-left: 0;
                font-size: 18px;
                text-align: center;
                white-space: nowrap;
            }
            h3 {
                padding-left: 0;
                font-size: 15px;

                font-size: 15px;
                font-weight: 500;
                padding-left: 14px;
                padding-right: 14px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="cont">
        <img src="me.png" class="loai">
        <div class="column">
            <h1>Hi, I'm Loai Khalid And This Is My Portfolio.</h1>
            <h3>With Extensive Experience In Website Development, I Specialize In Crafting Innovative, User-Friendly Websites. My Expertise Spans Front-End And Back-End Technologies, Ensuring Seamless Performance And a Polished, Modern Design Tailored To Client Needs.</h3>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
